        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "显示器连接至计算机等设备",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            53,
            42,
            584,
            77
        ],
        "page_idx": 6
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/885fd1d2e688a2805bf449000e7ead38b59186ef7bf6671764c2940417d54b43.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "content": "Line drawing of a desktop computer setup with monitor, tower, and power outlet (no text or symbols)",
        "sub_type": "natural_image",
        "bbox": [
            181,
            147,
            769,
            318
        ],
        "page_idx": 6
    },
    {
        "type": "list",
        "sub_type": "text",
        "list_items": [
            "1 将 HDMI 线缆或 VGA 线缆一端接入显示器的 HDMI 接口或 VGA 接口，另一端接入计算机的 HDMI 接口或 VGA 接口。",
            "2 将显示器和计算机的电源线等其他线缆连接好后开机，显示器屏幕上显示计算机的屏幕画面，代表连线成功。"
        ],
        "bbox": [
            68,
            379,
            929,
            461
        ],
        "page_idx": 6
    },
    {
        "type": "page_number",
